summary: This warrant allows the holder to buy a certain number of Favo Capital, Inc.'s common shares at $0.40 per share from September 16, 2024, until September 16, 2029. The warrant can be exercised by submitting a notice and payment, and it includes a cashless exercise option if specific conditions are met. Definitions and terms are detailed in the related Securities Purchase Agreement dated September 16, 2024.
